       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. T6CL05.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-CALENDAR.
           05  WS-DAY-ENTRY OCCURS 31 TIMES.
               10  WS-BUSINESS-FLAG PIC X VALUE 'N'.
                   88  BUSINESS-DAY VALUE 'Y'.
       01  WS-STATE.
           05  WS-DAYS-OBSERVED      PIC 9(2) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-SCAN-INDEX         PIC 9(2) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-BUSINESS-COUNT     PIC 9(2) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-CHARGE-DAYS        PIC S9(3) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-PENALTY            PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE ZERO.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-DAYS-OBSERVED
           PERFORM 2400-SCAN-CALENDAR
           DISPLAY WS-PENALTY
           STOP RUN.
       2400-SCAN-CALENDAR.
           PERFORM VARYING WS-SCAN-INDEX FROM 1 BY 1
              UNTIL WS-SCAN-INDEX > WS-DAYS-OBSERVED
              IF BUSINESS-DAY(WS-SCAN-INDEX)
                 ADD 1 TO WS-BUSINESS-COUNT
              END-IF
           END-PERFORM
           COMPUTE WS-CHARGE-DAYS = WS-BUSINESS-COUNT - 7
           IF WS-CHARGE-DAYS > ZERO
              COMPUTE WS-PENALTY = 500 * WS-CHARGE-DAYS
           END-IF.
